Package it.polimi.ingsw.observer

Interface ModelObserver

All Known Implementing Classes:
RMIObserver, SocketObserver
public interface ModelObserver
A class can implement the ModelObserver interface when it wants to be informed of changes in observable objects. It is implemented by SocketObserver and RMIObserver
